    • Method Detail

      • register

        void register(long raw,
            long offsetStart,
            long offsetEnd)
        Register a block that is fully closed.
        Parameters:
        raw - The size of block in terms of uncompressed bytes.
        offsetStart - The start offset of the block.
        offsetEnd - One byte after the end of the block. Compressed block size is offsetEnd - offsetStart.
